<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>The <link linkend="_class_k_t_n_1_1_algo_service_broker_v3">AlgoServiceBrokerV3</link> class routes messages to and from child instances of <link linkend="_class_k_t_n_1_1_algo_base_v3">AlgoBaseV3</link>. </para>



<para>This class provides functionality for initializing ZeroMQ, printing information, stopping all algorithms, resetting positions, sending commands, and handling algorithm commands and orders. </para>
</section>
